Vigil — Hermes post_llm_call Notification Plugin
===============================================

This plugin is derived from [hermes-notification](https://github.com/itgoyo/hermes-notification),
originally licensed under the MIT License.

Original Copyright (c) itgoyo

Changes from the upstream version:
- Removed min_response_length filtering
- Removed web-ui auto-detection and click-to-jump
- Removed configurable terminal_name
- Title prefix is configurable (title_prefix), default "vigil"
- Added tmux awareness: session:window.pane in title, notifications grouped by pane
